OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the evening with clear periods.
OL,7,FMost places staying frost free as
OL,8,Fcloud moves in from the north just
OL,9,Fbefore dawn, bringing some showers and
OL,10,Fstrengthening winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,13,Fscattered blustery showers, the
OL,14,Fshowers locally heavy with some strong
OL,15,Fgusts, mainly around coasts. Chilly,
OL,16,Fwith temperatures below average for
OL,17,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
